{"tid":1671704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四句就可以解釋到蔡英文禁止陳同佳「自由行」","createTime":"2019-10-23T15:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T16:16:14.000Z","uid":335157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4305642d1765bef68e02b59111cbd1247ef9c82c","tid":1671704,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"1.台灣從來都係主權國家，並不是逃犯條例修訂中 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中華人民共和國其他部分</span></span>。 （主要原因）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.正常移交逃犯程序（非協議國家）是交由立法會審議，並非透過修例處理殺人案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.將《刑事事宜相互法律協助條例》/司法互助（台灣）只加入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國/台灣地區</span></span> 既可以釋除公眾疑慮，又可以防止港台之間跨境犯罪，堵塞法律漏洞，即刻解決台灣殺人案。（都係主權問題，司法互助屬於政府與政府之間的合作，合作=承認）<br />\n<br />\n4.選票問題"},{"pid":"201157a8b0a57f84f82f492c29987a1b8574c9bb","tid":1671704,"uid":335157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補翻張圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2ArPLM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2ArPLM.png&h=2f4e00da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f3d6568a1a2690ecc41ecaac4aa2f3963d2f23","tid":1671704,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"只有逮捕沒有自首根本on9 啦"},{"pid":"fe013053f97680ec719b8386f8cbfc00cdcec950","tid":1671704,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33f3d6568a1a2690ecc41ecaac4aa2f3963d2f23","tid":1671704,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"只有逮捕沒有自首根本on9 啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"有乜咁on 9?&nbsp;&nbsp;投案唔係自首喎"},{"pid":"194eb49b8da6068bf2cf0adc95c093796145a37d","tid":16